"wp-block-heading">About Our DnD Name Generator</h2><p>Master the Dungeon=
=E2=80=99s DnD Name Generator is a list based generator. We don=E2=80=99t r=
am prefixes and suffixes together to make weird combinations. That being sa=
id, this name generator relies on all sorts of name data from from multiple=
 sources to give you the best names for your Dungeons and Dragons character=
.</p><p>Fantasy names often have their root within medieval <a href=3D"http=
s://www.masterthedungeon.com/creating-history-world/">history</a>. This is =
especially true for our human names list, as we use a lot of medieval names=
 as well as names taken from recent census data.</p><p>For fantasy races we=
 pull most of our names from classic fantasy literature and role playing so=
urces (including The Player=E2=80=99s Handbook) which in turn have their ow=
n structure. <a href=3D"https://www.masterthedungeon.com/dnd-character-name=
s/">Character names</a> are incredibly hard to think of on the fly because =
so often you need to know common names for the world you=E2=80=99re playing=
 in before you can pull something off the top of your head. To learn more r=
ead our post on <a href=3D"https://www.masterthedungeon.com/dnd-names/" tar=
get=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">How to Create Good Character Nam=
es</a>.</p><h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Helping Out and Future Updates</h=
2><p>We hope that you find this DnD Name Generator useful. If you like this=
 project and want to see more tools like this, the best way you can <a href=
=3D"https://www.masterthedungeon.com/in-support-of-supporters/">support</a>=
 us is by sharing this with your friends. If people like and use this tool =
we will continue to update and expand it.</p><p>We=E2=80=99ll even be able =
to add more tools like it to our site. We really enjoy creating things like=
